Subject: [Caml-list] OCaml-Top release 1.0.0

OCamlPro is proud to announce the release of OCaml-Top 1.0.0

OCaml-Top is an interactive editor targeted at education, with a simple and convenient interface:
an edition panel, with syntax coloration and automatic indentation, tightly coupled with an ocaml toplevel to easily evaluate the code as you go.

It is available from OPAM and as a binary installer for Windows.

OCaml-Top is released under the terms of the GNU GPL v3.

Home page: http://typerex.org/ocaml-top.html
Source on Github: https://github.com/OCamlPro/ocaml-top


We hope you appreciate it, and it gives a better experience to students and first-time users, especially on Windows.


Louis Gesbert -- OCamlPro
